---
title: Thai Pork & Mushroom Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice
description: This dish is an irresistible combination of courgette, tasty pork and garlicky rice, with the feel-good factor of cooking a filling meal from scratch. The best part is the addition of aromatic ginger to make it super satisfying.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-mushroom-stir-fry-1f9f38b6.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/pork-mushroom-stir-fry-5f7e609e55eb41083f7ce423-44f4744f.pdf
servings: 2
time required: 30 minutes
